    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1931-02-02T03:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1931-02-02T03:00:00-05:00" n="849"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d849">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/11356: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul General at Hankow</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Lockhart</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Hankow</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-02-02T16:00:00+08:00"
                            >February 2, 1931—4 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received February 2—9:25 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>8. The following telegram has been sent to the Legation: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“February 2, 3 p.m. <hi rend="italic">Panay</hi>
                            <note n="10" xml:id="d849fn10">U. S. river gunboat of the Yangtze
                                patrol.</note> and S. S. <hi rend="italic">Ichang</hi>, of Yangtze
                            Rapid Company fired upon at Temple Hill January 30. <hi rend="italic"
                                >Panay</hi> returned fire with 11 rounds 3-inch shells. No
                            casualties on <hi rend="italic">Panay</hi> or steamship. Repeated to
                            Department.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lockhart</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
